data.description:
PRICE REDUCTION + $5K SELLER CONCESSIONS     * ZERO ELECTRICITY BILLS* with solar panels. * Unincorporated from the city
Welcome to your peaceful oasis just outside the city limits of Alvord! This charming 3-2 double-wide mobile home sits on a sprawling 4.7-acre lot, offering a perfect blend of comfort, space, and tranquility.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the spacious open concept layout, complete with a cozy gas fireplace for those cold winter nights. 
Enjoy the serene outdoors from your beautiful covered front patio or entertain on the large back deck. The property is fenced and cross-fenced, providing security and privacy. A pond and a creek at the back of the property add to the natural charm, creating a picturesque landscape.
Other features include two barns, a hay cover structure, storm shelter, water well, and no restrictions, perfect for a small farm.
The detached carport also provides additional storage space. All new appliances convey with the home.
